      <title>巴基斯坦立法者修改宪法以增强影响力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-21/pakistan-lawmakers-change-constitution-to-strengthen-influence</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴基斯坦执政联盟于周一凌晨批准了一系列宪法修改，通过削减最高司法机构任命其首脑的权力来显示其议会的实力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-21/pakistan-lawmakers-change-constitution-to-strengthen-influence</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 07:20:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
