      <title>印度关键州准备投票之际莫迪强调稳定</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-21/modi-touts-stability-as-key-states-prepare-to-vote-in-india</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度总理纳伦德拉·莫迪表示，最近的选举胜利表明选民选择该国的政治连续性，两个关键邦准备在未来几周举行投票。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-21/modi-touts-stability-as-key-states-prepare-to-vote-in-india</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 07:20:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
