    <item>
      <title>莫桑比克世界顶级红宝石矿因“虚假”通知遭强行封矿</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-20/mozambique-police-shoot-two-as-gemfields-ruby-mine-is-stormed</link>
      <description><![CDATA[首席执行官肖恩·吉尔伯森 (Sean Gilbertson) 表示，周日约有 300 人闯入 Gemfields Group Ltd. 位于莫桑比克的红宝石矿场，该矿场的红宝石产量约占全球总产量的一半。他说，有两人被警方开枪打伤。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-20/mozambique-police-shoot-two-as-gemfields-ruby-mine-is-stormed</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 20 Oct 2024 20:58:27 GMT</pubDate>
